Name: Swatch Out!
About the game: Discover all the colors in the Art Zone by surrounding creatures the same color as you! Make yourself red, blue, or yellow, and discover how to become orange, green, and purple. In this action title, quickly find the color you need, and avoid spikes, bouncers, and enemies as you travel throughout the colorful Art Zone! Bring a big palette, because you'll need the right tint and shade as well! -Draw shapes around enemies to defeat them. -Find the right color for the right enemies. -Mix colors to find the right color needed for each enemy. -Avoid bumpers, spikes, and projectiles from enemies. -Send enemies away with a sonic blast.
